-----------------------------------------
Notice Regarding NC Voter Data
-----------------------------------------
This software retrieves and processes public voter registration and voting
history data published by the NC State Board of Elections (NCSBE). That data
is subject to restrictions under North Carolina law independent of the software
license above.

Specifically, N.C.G.S. § 163-82.10(c) prohibits using voter registration
information for commercial solicitation — i.e., to advertise, sell, or offer
for sale any goods or services. This prohibition applies regardless of whether
a commercial license for this software has been obtained.

Use of this software to collect, store, or process NC voter data for commercial
solicitation purposes is prohibited by state law and is not authorized by any
license granted herein.
